    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1939-10-30T07:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1939-10-30T07:00:00-05:00" n="830"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d830">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">300.115(39) City of Flint/73: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_SLA1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-10-30T15:00:00+03:00"
                            >October 30, 1939—3 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received October 30—11:43 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>833. The press today contains no reference of [<hi rend="italic">to</hi>] the <hi
                        rend="italic">City of Flint</hi> or to the Department’s statement issued in
                    connection therewith. The <pb facs="1112" n="1006" xml:id="pg_1006"/>
                    Department’s telegram containing the text of the statement issued on the 28th,
                    which was apparently sent from Washington on the evening of that date, was not
                    delivered to the Embassy until 3:30 on the morning of the 30th, having been held
                    up by the Soviet telegraph authorities.<note n="92" xml:id="d830fn92">This
                        statement was sent to the Embassy in telegram No. 217, October 29, 1939,
                        3:35 p.m. For the text of the statement, see Department of State, <hi
                            rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, vol. <hi rend="smallcaps">i</hi>, p. 431.
                        For other press releases regarding the <hi rend="italic">City of Flint</hi>,
                        issued by the Department of State, see <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, pp.
                        429–432, 457–458, and 556.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_SLA1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Steinhardt</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
